  <div id="gen-banner">
    <img src="/staticImages/Furniture-1-1.jpg" alt="Furniture image">
    <div id="g-banner-text">
      <h1>Interior, exterior design and 3D visualization in EU</h1>
      <p>ARTROOM is a team of professionals. We design flats, cottages, restaurants, bars, offices, shops, and other residential and public premises.</p>
      <p>We also develop individual projects for low-rise private residential buildings and perform architectural 3D visualisation.</p>
      <p>We have a huge number of successfully completed projects and many years of experience in this field. The specialists in our studio will prepare for you detailed technical documentation of the highest quality, so you can fully implement the object.</p>
    </div>
