    <div class="advantages-item">
      <img src="/staticImages/access-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="" width="60px" height="60px">
      <h2>A PERSONALISED APPROACH</h2>
      <p>Individual approach to each customer, rather than imposing their perceptions</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item">
      <img src="/staticImages/building-plan.svg" alt="" width="60px" height="60px">
      <h2>FULL SERVICE PACKAGE</h2>
      <p>Full service package from drawings to authoring</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item">
      <img src="/staticImages/building-tool-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="" width="60px" height="60px">
      <h2>3D VISUALISATION</h2>
      <p>High-quality and realistic 3D visualisation</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item">
      <img src="/staticImages/building.svg" alt="" width="60px" height="60px">
      <h2>FROM THE ROOM TO THE WHOLE SITE</h2>
      <p>The possibility of ordering the interior design of the entire property or of an individual room</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item">
      <img src="/staticImages/construction-worker-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="" width="60px" height="60px">
      <h2>CONSTRUCTION TEAMS</h2>
      <p>Possibility of realising the project with our construction crews</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item">
      <img src="/staticImages/science-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="" width="60px" height="60px">
      <h2>TECHNOLOGY</h2>
      <p>Use of innovative engineering technology and the latest construction materials in the design project</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item">
      <img src="/staticImages/quality-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="" width="60px" height="60px">
      <h2>QUALITY</h2>
      <p>The quality of our work is confirmed by the recommendations of our customers</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advantages-item">
      <img src="/staticImages/question-circle-svgrepo-com.svg" alt="" width="60px" height="60px">
      <h2>FREE CONSULTATIONS</h2>
      <p>Free advice from highly qualified professionals when buying a flat, plot or house, or when carrying out a design project.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

